				<p>So I tried to make this today and I think I&#8217;m going to have to give it another good in a few days because I don&#8217;t think I got it quite right. Now I think it tastes wonderful, but I don&#8217;t think I got the texture quite right. I had a huge problem after I processed the peanuts. I got it to the consistency of melted peanut butter (which was liquefied to me) but then in the time that I paused to add the other ingredients the peanuts must have solidified because my food processor just would not incorporate all the ingredients. Neither would my blender. I ended up putting it all in a bowl and used a spatula to fold it all together. So it looks like Nuetella but I&#8217;m pretty sure I don&#8217;t have the lovely smooth texture.</p>
